        "role": "assistant",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "I'm ready to help! I'm Claude Code, your AI coding assistant. \n\nI can help you with a wide variety of software engineering tasks, including:\n- **Writing and debugging code** in any programming language\n- **Exploring and analyzing** your codebase\n- **Refactoring and optimizing** code\n- **Building new features** or making changes to existing ones\n- **Running tests and commands** in your project\n- **Git operations** and version control\n- **Planning and designing** solutions for complex tasks\n- And much more!\n\nWhat would you like to work on? Feel free to describe your task, and I'll get started right away. If you need help with a specific file, feature, bug fix, or have any questions about your code, just let me know!"
          }
